Interface OraclePropertyGraphDatatypeConstants

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    OraclePropertyGraphConstants
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HBaseCommon, OraclePropertyGraph, OraclePropertyGraphBase

    public interface OraclePropertyGraphDatatypeConstants
    This interface defines the data type encoding supported in Property Graph
